  <brief_title>Novofine Autocover Safety Needle Versus BD Safety Glide</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Multi-Center, Prospective Cross-Over Study of Preference and Safety of NovoFine® Autocover(TM) Needles Compared to BD Safety Glide (TM) Syringes in the Hospital Setting</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Novo Nordisk A/S</agency>
